channel.title: Interface Editor

item.title: Interface Editor
item.dc:creator: @badger41 badger41
item.description:
@badger41 wrote:

i dont think you quite understand, the interface data is the same, the interface editor cant open your cache because its simply too big.

All you need to do is edit in a default 377 cache, the editor will export a data file that has all the interface data inside of it, you pack this file in interface.jag > data.dat

use tom’s cache suite

Read full topic
